1
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:35,750
(Destiny and Saving)

2
00:01:35,770 --> 00:01:38,610
(Episode 2)

3
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,080
This is the Mount Wuya.

4
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,759
It's so desolate.

5
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,759
I think even Yinhua Palace is better than this.

6
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,080
Well,

7
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,320
you stay here.

8
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,440
I'll go first.

9
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:58,080
What exactly are you looking at?

10
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:03,470
It's the Milky Way.

11
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:06,760
So you brought me here to see the Milky Way.

12
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,639
And you were keeping me in suspense.

13
00:02:09,210 --> 00:02:11,820
Tonight, the twenty-eight constellations are resetting their positions.

14
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:14,080
It’s a once-in-a-millennium event in the world.

15
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,880
You're very lucky

16
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,730
to have witnessed it.

17
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:20,180
Will all the High Immortals come?

18
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,000
They are not as lucky.

19
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:24,760
They will all go to the shore of the Four Seas.

20
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:27,840
This place used to be where I cultivated.

21
00:02:28,890 --> 00:02:30,070
No one will come here.

22
00:02:32,650 --> 00:02:34,600
So this is where you cultivated.

23
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:36,610
This place is so desolate.

24
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,960
No wonder you're such a bore.

25
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,540
It's beautiful.

26
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:47,490
When I was little,

27
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:50,520
my sister often took me to the peak of Danxue Mountain

28
00:02:51,070 --> 00:02:52,320
to see the meteor shower.

29
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,040
But the heavens and earth are vast,

30
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,200
we could only see

31
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,640
a few scattered stars.

32
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:01,760
Now,

33
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,680
it’s my first time seeing

34
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:05,360
this magnificent meteor shower.

35
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,720
Thank you,

36
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,040
Bai Yan.

37
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,480
That’s disrespectful.

38
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,760
Call me Master.

39
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,200
Bai Yan.

40
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,520
Master.

41
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:19,000
Bai Yan.

42
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,120
How many times have I told you?

43
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,280
You should call me Mas...

44
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:46,040
The meteor shower over the sea is spectacular.

45
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,650
It's obvious at a glance.

46
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,160
Lord Taibai.

47
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,320
Divine Lord Yuanyou.

48
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,680
Didn’t you go to see the meteor shower?

49
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:01,600
I have something on my mind.

50
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,800
I'm not in the mood to enjoy the view.

51
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,200
I'm waiting for you here

52
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,440
to seek advice on a matter.

53
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:10,400
May I ask what matter Divine Lord Yuanyou is referring to?

54
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:13,040
Today, I was reading through the ancient texts.

55
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:15,600
A thousand years ago, in the great war between immortals and demons,

56
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,959
the High Immortal of the Winged Clan Yu Qing committed a transgression,

57
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,880
and her clansmen were exiled from the divine race.

58
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,480
Nothing further was recorded.

59
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,200
Do you remember

60
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,800
whether the High Immortal Yu Qing

61
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,320
has any blood relatives?

62
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,440
Divine Lord Yuanyou,

63
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,400
why do you suddenly want to investigate

64
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,800
that matter from so long ago?

65
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:36,840
I'm in charge of patrolling Lijing Heaven.

66
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,800
Now that the God of War has returned,

67
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,960
I'm afraid the Asura Clan may again seek to get the token.

68
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:43,960
So I’m tracing things back to the root

69
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,360
to prevent trouble before it arises.

70
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:50,080
Divine Lord Yuanyou, you are right.

71
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:53,880
Back then, Yu Qing fell in love with the Demon Lord of the Asura Clan,

72
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,560
which led to a great disaster.

73
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:59,840
Her true form was that of the Winged Clan’s Sovereign.

74
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,640
She did have a younger sister,

75
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:03,600
raised since childhood on Danxue Mountain.

76
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:06,000
But she was very young at the time,

77
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,600
I don't know what she looks like now.

78
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,440
She has a sister?

79
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,680
Yes.

80
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:18,880
Please take a look.

81
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:22,240
Azure Spirit Feather.

82
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,720
Isn't this...

83
00:05:24,050 --> 00:05:26,440
the Spirit Feather of the Primordial Lord?

84
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,960
How did it end up with you?

85
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,720
After saying goodbye to Qing He,

86
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,760
I'll escort you to the Immortal Realm.

87
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,720
Greetings, General God of War.

88
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,600
The Heavenly Emperor has ordered.

89
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,560
General God of War, please take your disciple Nihuang

90
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,920
to Lingxiao Palace for questioning immediately.

91
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,600
-Bai Yan
-Nihuang.

92
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,600
Greetings, Your Majesty.

93
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,159
Bai Yan.

94
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,280
Take a look at this object.

95
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,640
Do you recognize it?

96
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,720
I once saw the Hundred-Feather Spirit Fan

97
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,200
in Divine Lord Yuanyou’s possession.

98
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,760
Then do you recognize

99
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,680
the Azure Spirit Feather

100
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,600
on this fan?

101
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,720
Your Majesty.

102
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,000
I do not recognize it.

103
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,200
Your Majesty.

104
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,480
The Azure Spirit Feather

105
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:56,520
belonged to the Primordial Lord Yu Qing.

106
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:58,620
During the great battle between immortals and demons a thousand years ago,

107
00:06:58,730 --> 00:07:00,650
when the High Immortal Yu Qing perished,

108
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,040
you were there.

109
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:04,410
How is it that today you claim not to remember?

110
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,000
The battle was intense at the time.

111
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,320
I only wanted to protect the Thousand Years Token.

112
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,880
I paid no attention to anything else.

113
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,090
The Hundred-Feather Spirit Fan

114
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,280
was found outside the barrier of Lijing Heaven

115
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,600
and came into Divine Lord Yuanyou’s possession.

116
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:18,910
Ever since you woke up from Lijing Heaven,

117
00:07:19,090 --> 00:07:23,250
haven't you sensed any unusual activity?

118
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,280
Your Majesty.

119
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,240
When I left Lijing Heaven,

120
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,560
I thoroughly inspected both the seal and the barrier.

121
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,000
Divine Lord Yuanyou has been patrolling many times.

122
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,800
No anomalies were ever discovered.

123
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,280
Bai Yan.

124
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,480
Don’t you think it’s rather strange

125
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:39,300
that a fan containing Yu Qing’s spirit feather

126
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,650
just happened to

127
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:43,620
appear outside the barrier

128
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,320
at the exact time you awakened?

129
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,120
And this immortal.

130
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,920
You were inside Lijing Heaven at the time as well.

131
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,640
Didn’t you notice anything?

132
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:56,159
Even the True Dragon God of War didn't notice,

133
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,560
how could someone

134
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:59,100
with my meager cultivation sense anything at all?

135
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,120
If that's the case,

136
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,160
it is indeed strange.

137
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:04,850
Your Majesty.

138
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,320
If the Asura Clan from Demon Realm

139
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,960
coveted the Thousand Years Token again

140
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,680
and tried to bring

141
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,840
the Demon Lord and the High Immortal Yu Qing back to life,

142
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,600
and then we have to

143
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,560
investigate this matter thoroughly.

144
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:18,680
The Thousand Years Token can bring people back to life?

145
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,880
May I borrow it for use?

146
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,040
Nihuang.

147
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,040
Bai Yan.

148
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,440
What kind of disciple have you taken in,

149
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:27,340
to dare speak such outrageous words?

150
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,000
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

151
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:30,800
Nihuang is new to the Heavenly Palace.

152
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,680
She doesn’t yet understand propriety.

153
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,200
Maybe

154
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,760
she was only thinking about her affected clansmen.

155
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,380
I ask for your forgiveness, Your Majesty.

156
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,799
Affected clansmen?

157
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,360
Who are they?

158
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:48,680
The aquatic beings beneath the ice plains.

159
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,400
Bai Yan.

160
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,680
You are the True Dragon God of War.

161
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:56,320
You have never shown favoritism towards your disciples before.

162
00:08:56,880 --> 00:09:00,400
Why are you always protecting this little koi fish?

163
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,520
Is that

164
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:04,680
you have some untold difficulties?

165
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,880
Your Majesty.

166
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,400
I'm not being partial to my disciple.

167
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,360
It's just that...

168
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
I fell in love with Nihuang

169
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,240
at first sight.

170
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:35,920
Bai Yan.

171
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,680
You must know that

172
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,000
you cultivated for ten thousand years on Mount Wuya.

173
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:44,600
You are the True Dragon God of War trained by the Father God.

174
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,320
Your destiny

175
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,680
is to serve the Three Realms

176
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,720
and fight for the Three Realms.

177
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,320
Now,

178
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:55,280
you fell in love with a little immortal.

179
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,680
How can the safety of the Three Realms

180
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:59,040
still rest upon your shoulders?

181
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:01,500
How can you possibly bear

182
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:05,200
the title of True Dragon God of War earned over millennia?

183
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,240
If you really think of him as the True Dragon God of War,

184
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,560
then don't insult him.

185
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,800
Must the True Dragon God of War

186
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:12,480
be nothing but a weapon of the Three Realms?

187
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,880
Does he not deserve a body of flesh and blood?

188
00:10:14,020 --> 00:10:15,720
Is he not allowed to feel love and longing?

189
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,560
-Shut up!
-You...

190
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,000
How dare you

191
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,120
offend the Heavenly Emperor’s authority?

192
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:22,440
You clearly have no regard for the laws of the Nine Heavens.

193
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,730
Disrespectful!

194
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:28,000
I've never seen such a reckless minor immortal.

195
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,240
Nihuang.

196
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,600
This is the Heavenly Palace.

197
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:32,020
Watch your words.

198
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,360
I am not a minor immortal,

199
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,960
nor a koi fish.

200
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,880
I am the Fire Phoenix of Danxue Mountain,

201
00:10:37,900 --> 00:10:39,460
the sister of the High Immortal Yu Qing,

202
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:40,570
Nihuang.

203
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,360
I had no intention of intruding into Lijing Heaven.

204
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,160
I thought he was a trapped white snake,

205
00:10:45,180 --> 00:10:46,180
so I saved him.

206
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,400
The reason I stayed in the Heavenly Palace

207
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,480
was only to find my Hundred-Feather Spirit Fan.

208
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:53,960
My Fire Phoenix clan was once part of the divine race.

209
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:56,430
Even if the True Dragon God of War has feelings for me,

210
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,680
I don't feel that I am unworthy.

211
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,400
Your Majesty.

212
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,520
This reckless demon woman

213
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,920
hid her true identity,

214
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:05,320
broke into Lijing Heaven,

215
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,120
damaged the Thousand Years Token’s barrier,

216
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,240
and infiltrated the Heavenly Palace.

217
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,280
All these actions are highly suspicious.

218
00:11:10,580 --> 00:11:11,780
This concerns the Thousand Years Token,

219
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,160
Your Majesty, I request you to make a clear judgment.

220
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:14,960
Your Majesty.

221
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,520
Nihuang is not at fault at all.

222
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,800
The fault lies with me.

223
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,800
Hiding Nihuang’s true identity

224
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,840
was entirely my idea.

225
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,980
Back then, Yu Qing sacrificed her Core

226
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,600
to perish together with Xuan Yi,

227
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:30,080
bringing an end to the war between immortals and demons.

228
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,470
Her intentions were always for the sake of the beings of the Three Realms,

229
00:11:32,490 --> 00:11:33,770
not to defy the Heavenly Way.

230
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,320
It has always been the Asura Clan

231
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,860
that coveted the Thousand Years Token.

232
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:41,070
The Winged Clan was cast out of the divine race due to Yu Qing’s punishment.

233
00:11:41,090 --> 00:11:42,510
For all these years, they have

234
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,000
remained dutiful and content.

235
00:11:44,130 --> 00:11:45,410
They have not uttered a single complaint.

236
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:48,160
As for Nihuang, she acted out of sisterly love

237
00:11:48,650 --> 00:11:50,000
to find Yu Qing’s Core

238
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,240
and accidentally entered Lijing Heaven.

239
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,640
Fearing she might repeat Yu Qing’s tragic fate,

240
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,640
I kept her at my side

241
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:57,750
to verify her intentions.

242
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,080
I am willing to stake my divine position

243
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,360
to vouch for her to you.

244
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,920
Nihuang is just naive and ignorant.

245
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,360
Driven only by the desire to save her sister.

246
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,760
She has absolutely no desire for the Thousand Years Token.

247
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,160
Your Majesty, please see the truth clearly.

248
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:15,000
Nihuang is just an ordinary Fire Phoenix.

249
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,520
She has been by my side,

250
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,440
and after observing her for several days,

251
00:12:20,010 --> 00:12:21,680
I’ve found her nature to be pure and kind.

252
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:23,930
She would never harm the Three Realms.

253
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,300
Your Majesty,

254
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,720
please send Nihuang back to Danxue Mountain.

255
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:30,960
Bai Yan.

256
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,120
Let me ask you this.

257
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,680
If she is merely an ordinary Fire Phoenix,

258
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:37,800
how could she have the power to break through the barrier of Lijing Heaven?

259
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,520
If she escapes this time,

260
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,700
and later harbors ill intent toward the Thousand Years Token，

261
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,560
won’t we have left a great threat behind?

262
00:12:45,010 --> 00:12:46,280
-Right.
-Right.

263
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,260
We can't take this risk.

264
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:50,310
We can't take it lightly.

265
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:52,600
Your Majesty.

266
00:12:52,780 --> 00:12:54,920
Whether this demon woman is hiding divine power,

267
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:57,320
we will know the truth by casting her into the Honghuang well.

268
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,040
No way!

269
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,280
Your Majesty.

270
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:00,760
Nihuang’s cultivation is still shallow.

271
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:02,040
If she enters the Honghuang well,

272
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,080
she will surely face endless torment,

273
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,720
and is going to be erased forever.

